  </text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="390.4" y="459.2" textLength="390.4" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">uninstall.&#160;If&#160;you&#x27;d&#160;like&#160;to&#160;use&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="780.8" y="459.2" textLength="36.6" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">pip</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="817.4" y="459.2" textLength="280.6" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">&#160;instead,&#160;just&#160;replace&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="1098" y="459.2" textLength="48.8" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">pipx</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="1146.8" y="459.2" textLength="73.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">&#160;with&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="1220" y="459.2" textLength="36.6" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">pip</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="1256.6" y="459.2" textLength="671" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">&#160;in&#160;the&#160;below&#160;command.&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r1" x="1952" y="459.2" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-18)">
