  </text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r1" x="1952" y="654.4" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-26)">
  </text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="390.4" y="678.8" textLength="305" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">If&#160;you&#x27;re&#160;looking&#160;to&#160;use&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="695.4" y="678.8" textLength="73.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">browsr</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="768.6" y="678.8" textLength="793" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">&#160;on&#160;remote&#160;file&#160;systems,&#160;like&#160;AWS&#160;S3,&#160;you&#x27;ll&#160;need&#160;to&#160;install&#160;the&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="1561.6" y="678.8" textLength="73.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">remote</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="1634.8" y="678.8" textLength="292.8" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">&#160;extra.&#160;If&#160;you&#x27;d&#160;like&#160;to</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r1" x="1952" y="678.8" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-27)">
  </text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="390.4" y="703.2" textLength="597.8" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">browse&#160;parquet&#160;files,&#160;you&#x27;ll&#160;need&#160;to&#160;install&#160;the&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="988.2" y="703.2" textLength="85.4" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">parquet</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="1073.6" y="703.2" textLength="561.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">&#160;extra.&#160;Or,&#160;even&#160;simpler,&#160;you&#160;can&#160;install&#160;the&#160;</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r13" x="1634.8" y="703.2" textLength="36.6" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">all</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r5" x="1671.4" y="703.2" textLength="256.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">&#160;extra&#160;to&#160;get&#160;all&#160;the</text><text class="terminal-1821857073-r1" x="1952" y="703.2" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-1821857073-line-28)">
